{
  "texts": [
    "We built a User Interface for crowd workers to engage in direct conversations with the GPT-3 model.",
    "The interface integrates GPT-3 API, enabling real-time responses to our participants.",
    "To ensure a diverse participant pool, we implemented screening questions and conducted pilot testing to gain insights into the demographic distribution of the online crowdsourcing platform.",
    "We briefly describe our algorithm auditing design for data collection, measurements for user experience, methods for analyzing human-AI dialogues, as well as our statistical models to address the three RQs.",
    "Further details are provided in the Online Supplemental Information (SI)."
  ]
}